<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <h1>HIG UX KIT : Multiselect Tag / Pill</h1>
    <ul>
      <li>NPM Package: <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/chosen-js" target="_blank">ChosenJS Package</a></li>
      <li>For more information, please navigate to <a href="https://github.com/harvesthq/chosen">ChosenJS Github</a></li>
      <li><b>Note: </b>Be cautious with using the dropdown tag with a long list. If you were to put the selected tags on top/bottom/side then you might have to make adjustments programmatically.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
